wikipedia_page.main:
Jenny Davis (born 1983 or 1984) is a Scottish racing cyclist from East Calder, West Lothian.
Davis is a Commonwealth Games silver medallist, coming second in the  Women’s Team Sprint in the Delhi 2010 Games.
